S.FORM: === u siwkay niza === Shu Qi (1976.4.16) tatayna, nalecuhan i Taywan. u tatengaay a ngangan sa ci Lin Lihuy. namaala ku yadahay a kawlah i iga atu tilibi. u sapuyaay a kakuniza u kawaw niza u sulit nu Hulam Lin Li-hui (Chinese:林立慧; pinyin: Lín Lìhuì; born 16 April 1976), better known by her stage name Shu Qi, is a Taiwanese actress and model. She is among the highest paid actresses in China u kawlah niza u uzip niza (amicunus henay tu sulit.待補充)

=== o siwkay niza === Sho Qi (1976.4.16) tatayna, nalecohan i Taywan. o tatengaay a ngangan sa ci Lin Lihoy. namaala ko yadahay a kawlah i iga ato tilibi. o sapoyaay a kakoniza o kawaw niza o solit no Holam Lin Li-hoi (Chinese:林立慧; pinyin: Lín Lìhoì; born 16 April 1976), better known by her stage name Sho Qi, is a Taiwanese actress and model. She is among the highest paid actresses in China o kawlah niza o ozip niza (amiconos henay to solit.待補充)
